ent focused equity portfolios the firm also launches and manages equity and balanced mutual funds and hedge funds for its clients it invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe the firm employs longonly and longshort strategies while creating its portfolios it employs fundamental and quantitative analysis along with a combination of topdown with the bottomup stock picking approaches while making its investments the firm was founded in  and is based in london united kingdom with an additional office in hong kong it was formerly known as veritas asset management uk limited as of october   veritas asset management llp operates as a subsidiary of affiliated managers group inc detailed description  long acrest floorlondon  wce raunited kingdomfounded in  phone     fax     wwwveritasassetcom key executives for veritas asset management llp mr ian barnes chief executive officer mr charles buchan richardson partner fund manager and chairman mr richard john grant partner and chief operating officer dr xuejun sun phd partner fund manager and head of asia mr andrew nicholas headley partner fund manager and head of global compensation as of fiscal year  veritas asset management llp key developments asia veritas asset management llp presents at morningstar investment conference  london  may  am apr   asia veritas asset management llp presents at morningstar investment conference  london  may  am venue park plaza riverbank hotel london united kingdom speakers ezra sun fund manager and head veritas asset management appoints ian barnes as chief executive effective early  sep   veritas asset management announced that ian barnes former head of ubs asset management for ireland and the uk has been appointed to the newly created position of chief executive he will join in early  becoming part of the managing partners board barnes had been head of asset management at ubs for uk and ireland since  before that he was at russell investments where his initial role a