ividend and will be more constrained in the stocks that can be bought the global real return strategy seeks to further protect the downside by the use of index derivativesexpandglobal strategiesveritas global focus characteristics– concentrated global equity portfolio  positions investing in mid to large capitalisation companies – fundamentally driven portfolio with an investment horizon of  years or a full economic cycle – identify and analyse only quality companies – value disciplined only invest when attractive real returns achievable – targeting annualised portfolios returns of oecd g cpi   pa over rolling  year periods – available as a segregated portfolio – available as a fund veritas global focus fund  veritas global focus common contractual fundexpandveritas global equity income characteristics– high and sustainable equity yield – concentrated global equity portfolio investing in mid to large capitalisation companies – fundamentally driven portfolio with an investment horizon of  years or a full economic cycle – identify and analyse only quality companies – value disciplined only invest when attractive real returns achievable – targeting annualised portfolios returns of oecd g cpi   pa over rolling  year periods – available as a segregated portfolio – available as a fund veritas global equity income fundexpandveritas global real return characteristics– concentrated global equity fund investing in mid to large capitalisation companies – fundamentally driven portfolio with an investment horizon of   years or a full economic cycle – identify and analyse only quality companies – value disciplined only invest when attractive real returns achievable – hedging through the use of index options and futures as appropriate – targeting annualised returns of oecd g cpi  pa over rolling  year periods – available as a fund veritas global real return fundexpandveritas izoard characteristics– highly concentrated global equity portfolio  positions investing in mid to large ca